Module Basics

Basic features such as mathematics and geometry functions, general containers, objects and utilities.
Author:
Jörg Roth (Joerg.Roth@Wireless-earth.org)

  • Packages

    Exports 
    Package Description
    basics.math
    Provides general access to all robot components and basic functions.
    basics.math.downhill
    Downhill optimization.
    basics.math.rot
    Mathematical functions for modelling rotations and translations.
    basics.math.solids
    Geometric computations on 3D solids.
    basics.obj
    This package provides basic objects, e.g. pair-objects.
    basics.util
    This package provides utility functions and containers.
